description: This file defines a React functional component named Navbar, which renders the top navigation bar of a web application. It includes links that vary depending on the user's login status, handles logout functionality, and uses React Router for navigation.

methods.name: Navbar({ user })
methods.description: React functional component that renders a navigation bar with links that depend on user login status and handles user logout.

methods.name: onLogout
methods.description: Asynchronous function to log the user out via dataService and then navigate to the login page.
